entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have met Captain Piett on Dathomir, he would like you to perform a job on behalf of the Empire.
entries.journal_entry_description: Darth Vader requests your presence on Dathomir.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: [Darth Vader] I have an important proposition for you. Meet Captain Piett on Dathomir immediately.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Speak with Captain Piett to see what is going on.
